# kCFCopyStringSetCallBacks

**Global Variable**

Predefined [doc://com.apple.corefoundation/documentation/CoreFoundation/CFSetCallBacks] structure containing a set of callbacks  appropriate for use when the values in a set are all CFString objects. The retain callback makes an immutable copy of strings added to the set.

## Declaration

```swift
let kCFCopyStringSetCallBacks: CFSetCallBacks
```

## Constants

- **kCFTypeSetCallBacks**
